OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry is 'engine for
OL,4,Cchange' and will not 'paper over
OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,FThe Southport Inquiry will act as a
OL,8,F"real engine for change" and will "not
OL,9,Fturn into an exercise of papering over
OL,10,Fthe cracks", the chair has promised as
OL,11,Fhe formally opened the hearing.
OL,13,FThe probe into 'one of the most
OL,14,Fhorrific crimes in the country's
OL,15,Fhistory' has been established to
OL,16,F"thoroughly investigate" the
OL,17,Fcircumstances around the deaths of
OL,18,Fthree girls at a Taylor Swift-themed
OL,19,Fdance class on 29 July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
