OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry is 'engine for
OL,4,Cchange' and will not 'paper over
OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,FIt will look at whether the attack,
OL,8,Fwhich killed Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,9,Fnine, Bebe King, six, and Elsie Dot
OL,10,FStancombe, seven, could or should have
OL,11,Fbeen prevented, given what was known
OL,12,Fabout the perpetrator - who is not
OL,13,Fbeing named "for the benefit of the
OL,14,Fvictims and their families".
OL,16,FChairman Sir Adrian Fulford, a former
OL,17,Fvice-president of the Court of Appeal,
OL,18,Fbegan proceedings with an opening
OL,19,Fstatement at a packed Liverpool Town
OL,20,FHall in front of families, lawyers and
OL,21,Fjournalists.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
