OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry is 'engine for
OL,4,Cchange' and will not 'paper over
OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,F"As the Government at the highest
OL,8,Flevels has recognised, the perpetrator
OL,9,Fis responsible for one of the most
OL,10,Fegregious crimes in our country's
OL,11,Fhistory," Sir Adrian said.
OL,13,F"However hard we try, ordinary
OL,14,Flanguage simply fails to reflect the
OL,15,Fenormity of what he did.
OL,17,F"None of the most powerful adjectives
OL,18,Feven begin to suffice: there are no
OL,19,Fwords that adequately describe what
OL,20,Foccurred."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
