OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,FThe perpetrator was given a life
OL,8,Fsentence in January, with a minimum
OL,9,Fterm of 52 years for the three
OL,10,Fmurders, one of the highest minimum
OL,11,Fterms on record when he was sentenced
OL,12,Fin January.
OL,14,FThe 18-year-old also attempted to
OL,15,Fmurder eight other children, who
OL,16,Fcannot be named for legal reasons, as
OL,17,Fwell as class instructor Leanne Lucas
OL,18,Fand businessman John Hayes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
