OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,FAhead of the hearing lawyers for the
OL,8,Ffamilies of Elsie, Alice and Bebe said
OL,9,Fthey would do "all we can to assist
OL,10,Fthe Chair... and uncover the truth".
OL,12,F"Ultimately as legal representatives
OL,13,Fof the bereaved families we are
OL,14,Fcommitted to getting answers for
OL,15,Fthem," Rachael Wong, Director at Bond
OL,16,FTurner, and the Recognised Legal
OL,17,FRepresentative for the three bereaved
OL,18,Ffamilies Chris Walker, also of Bond
OL,19,FTurner, said.
