OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry is 'engine for
OL,4,Cchange' and will not 'paper over
OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,F"We know that nothing the Inquiry
OL,8,Freveals, or subsequently recommends
OL,9,Fwill change the unimaginable loss felt
OL,10,Fby the families of Elsie, Alice and
OL,11,FBebe, but we all now have a
OL,12,Fresponsibility to ensure that
OL,13,Fsomething like this never happens
OL,14,Fagain.
OL,16,F"We will be doing all we can to assist
OL,17,Fthe Chair through the Inquiry and
OL,18,Funcover the truth.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
