OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry is 'engine for
OL,4,Cchange' and will not 'paper over
OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,F"It is only through intense public
OL,8,Fscrutiny that real change can be
OL,9,Feffected."
OL,11,FThe inquiry will be split into two
OL,12,Fphases, the first focusing on issues
OL,13,Faround policing, the criminal justice
OL,14,Fsystem and the multiple agencies
OL,15,Finvolved with the 18-year-old before
OL,16,Fthe attack.
OL,18,FThe second phase will examine the
OL,19,Fwider issue of young people being
OL,20,Fdrawn into extreme violence.
