OL,4,Cchange' and will not 'paper over
OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,FSpeaking of the first phase Sir Adrian
OL,8,Fsaid: "This will be necessarily wide
OL,9,Franging, encompassing the criminal
OL,10,Fjustice system, relevant events during
OL,11,Fhis education, his engagement with
OL,12,Fsocial and health care, his
OL,13,Frelationship with his family and much
OL,14,Felse besides."
OL,16,FHe added: "We need to understand what
OL,17,Fwent wrong and thereafter to identify
OL,18,Fand implement the most effective
OL,19,Fmeasures to ensure, to the extent that
OL,20,Fwe are able, that there is no
OL,21,Frepetition.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@NO]
