OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry is 'engine for
OL,4,Cchange' and will not 'paper over
OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,F"As a society we are not helpless when
OL,8,Fconfronted with individuals who are
OL,9,Fknown to be contemplating acts of such
OL,10,Fdepravity and although no solution
OL,11,Fwill be foolproof, we can identify all
OL,12,Fof the robust steps which should be
OL,13,Ftaken to protect ourselves, and
OL,14,Fparticularly the most vulnerable, from
OL,15,Fhorrors of this kind."
OL,17,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper announced
OL,18,Fthe public inquiry in January to help
OL,19,Funderstand what went wrong and prevent
OL,20,Fany repetition of similar incidents.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
