OL,4,Cchange' and will not 'paper over
OL,5,Ccracks'
OL,7,FThree separate referrals were made to
OL,8,Fthe Government's counter-terror
OL,9,Fprogramme Prevent about the
OL,10,Fperpetrator's behaviour in the years
OL,11,Fbefore the attack, as well as six
OL,12,Fseparate calls to police.
OL,14,FA review into the Prevent referrals
OL,15,Fpublished in February found there was
OL,16,Fsufficient risk posed by the killer to
OL,17,Fkeep his cases within Prevent active
OL,18,Fbut that these were closed prematurely
OL,19,Fwhile too much focus was placed on a
OL,20,Flack of distinct ideology.
