OL,7,FThe inquiry will draw on evidence from
OL,8,Finterviews with witnesses and
OL,9,Fdisclosure from 15 organisations,
OL,10,Fincluding MI5, Counter-Terrorism
OL,11,FPolicing, NHS England and Merseyside
OL,12,FPolice.
OL,14,FThe widespread rioting and civil
OL,15,Funrest following the murders is not
OL,16,Fbeing examined by the inquiry.
